      "id": "PopularPost12335",
      "post_content": "Red creatures don't really regenerate. This and Eron the Relentless are pretty much it for red creatures (that don't try to involve another color) that you can make regenerate. Red's burn has great synergy with this card, actually, and Uthden Troll is much better than it looks because of it. Hardly a bomb or anything, this troll plays much better than he looks (because he admittedly looks quite average).",
      "posted_by": "Malachorn",
